    "concept_sort_game": "inafanya kazi concept panga mchezo interface kwa categorization fanya mazoezi. Buruta kipengele into correct jamii buckets kwa demonstrate understanding ya classification concepts. Immediate feedback inaonyesha correct na incorrect placements. msaada 2-4 jamii na any nambari ya sortable kipengele. Great kwa msamiati tiers, science classifications, au grammar sorting.",
